# Setting.Bluetooth
### 界面类
##### 1.BluetoothSettings 
   	extends DeviceListPreferenceFragment //蓝牙设备显示
    extends RestrictedSettingsFragment // 有约束的设置项显示
    extends SettingsPreferenceFragment //设置项显示
    extends InstrumentedPreferenceFragment //Preference界面显示的工具
    extends PreferenceFragment
    extends Fragment
- 功能: 
	1. 显示蓝牙配置和连接，实现部分BluetoothCallback回调(Setting点击进入蓝牙设置的主界面)
```
public interface BluetoothCallback {
	//状态变化
    void onBluetoothStateChanged(int bluetoothState);
    //扫描状态
    void onScanningStateChanged(boolean started);
    //新设备加入
    void onDeviceAdded(CachedBluetoothDevice cachedDevice);
    //设备消失
    void onDeviceDeleted(CachedBluetoothDevice cachedDevice);
    //绑定状态变化
    void onDeviceBondStateChanged(CachedBluetoothDevice cachedDevice, int bondState);
    //连接状态变化
    void onConnectionStateChanged(CachedBluetoothDevice cachedDevice, int state);
}
```
	2. 显示OptionMenu,SwitchBar,PairedDevices,AvailableDevices的信息
	
##### DeviceListPreferenceFragment
	//包含Field: LocalBluetoothManager，LocalBluetoothAdapter
	//包含一个蓝牙设备列表?，实现蓝牙回调并注册到LocalBlueToothManager
	//preference监听
##### BluetoothDevicePreference 
	extends Preference 
	implements CachedBluetoothDevice.Callback, OnClickListener
	- 使用 cachedDevice info 构造一个用来显示的 Prefernce
	
### 工具类
##### LocalBluetoothPreferences.java 
	- 提供一些接口来操作SharePreference:bluetooth_settings的工具类
##### Utils.java 
	- contains constants for various,
	- Android resource IDs
	- debug logging flags 
	- static methods for creating dialogs.
##### Utf8ByteLengthFilter.java
	- filter for input text
##### RequestPermissionHelperActivity extends 
  AlertActivity extends 
  Activity
	- 功能: 
		- asks the user whether to enable discovery
		- 
	AlertActivity内部有一个AlertController和一个AlertParams成员变量，用来构建AlertView
		注:AlertController内部有一个AlertParems成员变量，也有一些初始化的Layout，因此可以构建View
		
##### DeviceProfilesSettings extends DialogFragment extends Fragment
	- 布局: device_profiles_settings.xml
	- 功能: 显示Paired devices 的 Dialog
##### BluetoothEnable.java
	- manage the Bluetooth on/off checkbox and state

  	
